        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Say No to Indoctrination Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the use of federal funds to teach or advance concepts that separate individuals based on race, color, or national origin; assign characteristics to individuals based on race, color, or national origin; or imply that the United States is an inherently racist country.</p>]]>
        </text>
